{"title_page": "Chapter One (Level 10 album)", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Chapter One\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[Level 10 (band)|Level 10]]\n| cover      = Level 10 Chapter One.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = January 23, 2015\n| recorded   = \n| venue      = United States, Germany, Italy\n| studio     = *Russell Allen Studio, South River, NJ; \n*Level 10 Studio, Ostfildern; \n*Guitarslinger Studio, Spiesen-Elversberg; \n*Ivorytears Music Works, Somma Lombardo\n| genre      = [[Heavy metal music|Heavy metal]]\n| length     = 53:02 <small>(International version)</small><br>56:34 <small>(Japanese version)</small>\n| label      = [[Frontiers Records]]\n| producer   = [[Mat Sinner]]\n| prev_title =\n| prev_year  =\n| next_title = \n| next_year  = \n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Chapter One\n | type        = studio\n | single1     = Blasphemy\n | single1date = December 15, 2014\n | single2     = Cry No More\n | single2date = January 23, 2015 \n}}\n}}\n\n'''''Chapter One''''' is the first album by project [[Level 10 (band)|Level 10]] featuring [[Symphony X]] and [[Adrenaline Mob]] vocalist [[Russell Allen]] and bassist/producer [[Mat Sinner]]. It was released via [[Frontiers Records]]<ref>{{cite web |title=LEVEL 10  CHAPTER 1 |url=http://www.frontiers.it/album/5236 |website=Frontiers Music Srl Record Label}}</ref> on January 23, 2015<ref>{{cite web |title=LEVEL 10 Featuring RUSSELL ALLEN, MAT SINNER: Debut Album 'Chapter One' Due In January |url=https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/level-10-featuring-russell-allen-mat-sinner-debut-album-chapter-one-due-in-january/ |website=Blabbermouth.net}}</ref> with ''Cry No More'' single lyric video<ref>{{cite web |title=LEVEL 10 Featuring RUSSELL ALLEN, MAT SINNER: 'Cry No More' Lyric Video |url=https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/level-10-featuring-russell-allen-mat-sinner-cry-no-more-lyric-video/ |website=Discogs}}</ref> and it was anticipated by single ''Blasphemy'' on December 15, 2014.<ref>{{cite web |title=LEVEL 10 Featuring RUSSELL ALLEN, MAT SINNER: 'Blasphemy' Lyric Video |url=https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/level-10-featuring-russell-allen-mat-sinner-blasphemy-lyric-video/ |website=Blabbermouth.net}}</ref>\n\nThe lineup is completed by drummer [[Randy Black]] and guitar players [[Alex Beyrodt]] of [[Primal Fear (band)|Primal Fear]], [[Roland Grapow]] of [[Masterplan (band)|Masterplan]] and [[Alessandro Del Vecchio]] ([[Hardline (band)|Hardline]], [[Jorn (band)|Jorn]], Edge of Forever) on keyboards.<ref>{{cite web |title=Chapter One Level 10 Lineup |url=https://www.metal-archives.com/albums/Level_10/Chapter_One/485573 |website=Encyclopaedia Metallum The Metal Archives}}</ref>\n\nThe album also features artists [[Amanda Somerville]], [[Carsten Schulz]], [[Magnus Karlsson (guitarist)|Magnus Karlsson]] and [[Sander Gommans]].\n\n==Track listing==\nAll songs written by [[Russell Allen]], [[Alex Beyrodt]], [[Sander Gommans]], [[Magnus Karlsson (guitarist)|Magnus Karlsson]], [[Carsten Schulz]], [[Mat Sinner]], [[Amanda Somerville]] and [[Alessandro Del Vecchio]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Level 10 Chapter One |url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/chapter-one-mw0002784936 |website=AllMusic}}</ref>\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed       = \n| headline        =\n| total_length    = 53:02\n| title1          = Cry No More\n| length1         = 4:23\n| writer1         =\n\n| title2          = Soul Of A Warrior\n| length2         = 5:49\n| writer2         =\n\n| title3          = When The Nighttime Comes\n| length3         = 4:05\n| writer3         =\n\n| title4          = One Way Street\n| length4         = 5:02\n| writer4         =\n\n| title5          = Blasphemy\n| length5         = 4:31\n| writer5         =\n\n| title6          = Last Man On Earth\n| length6         = 3:35\n| writer6         =\n\t\n| title7          = In For The Kill\n| length7         = 4:16\n| writer7         =\n\n| title8          = Voice Of The Wilderness\n| length8         = 4:22\n| writ